      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Poohead Card Game was an online multiplayer card game, which made the frontend inherently interactive and state-driven.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "I built the client in React while integrating with a server-side game engine workflow, creating a user experience built around multiplayer game interaction rather than static content.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "This project is useful proof of range: I am comfortable not only with product dashboards and fintech interfaces, but also with interaction-heavy frontend experiences.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
